    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Thubdora barbata (Meyrick): A, adult, holotype; B, ditto, lateral view; C, labels; D, male genitalia, holotype, gen. slide no. CIS-7136/Park; E, ditto, aedeagus; F, abdomen, with a pair of long hair-like pencils. Scale bar for the genitalia and aedeagus: 1.0 mm (same in the following figures)." ;
